04:06:51,000 --> 04:06:56,000
Just to check, we take 5-thirds times the first column of A,

2725
04:06:56,000 --> 04:06:59,000
minus 2-thirds times the second column of A,

2726
04:06:59,000 --> 04:07:03,000
and we indeed get 6, 7.

2727
04:07:03,000 --> 04:07:06,000
Yippee!

2728
04:07:06,000 --> 04:07:10,000
It's nice when things work like they're supposed to.

