04:07:10,000 --> 04:07:13,000
I use the same method for 3 by 3 system.

2730
04:07:13,000 --> 04:07:18,000
This time, you've got to compute a determinant for each of 3 variables,

2731
04:07:18,000 --> 04:07:21,000
