2735
04:07:34,000 --> 04:07:37,000
So again, take B, take the vector B,

2736
04:07:37,000 --> 04:07:39,000
stick it in the first column of A,

2737
04:07:39,000 --> 04:07:43,000
leave the rest of A alone, and compute that determinant.

2738
04:07:43,000 --> 04:07:47,000
Same thing, A sub 2 of B, we take B,

2739
04:07:47,000 --> 04:07:50,000
stick it in the second column of A,

2740
04:07:50,000 --> 04:07:53,000
and leave the rest of A alone, compute that determinant.

2741
04:07:53,000 --> 04:07:58,000
A sub 3 of B, we take the B,

2742
04:07:58,000 --> 04:08:01,000
replace the third column of A,

2743
04:08:01,000 --> 04:08:04,000
compute that determinant, and then put it all together.

