04:08:49,000 --> 04:08:51,000
So you have 5, 4 by 4 determinants,

2758
04:08:51,000 --> 04:08:53,000
and that would be a lot of work.

2759
04:08:53,000 --> 04:08:56,000
So this is not practical in a general sense,

2760
04:08:56,000 --> 04:09:03,000
but for theoretical and for small matrices like this,

2761
04:09:03,000 --> 04:09:06,000
