06:31:16,600 --> 06:31:19,720
And since that's a basis for the column space of B,

4601
06:31:19,720 --> 06:31:24,200
the blue line, or the x-axis, is the column space of B.

4602
06:31:24,200 --> 06:31:26,760
All multiples of 1, 0.

