06:31:26,760 --> 06:31:31,080
So clearly here, these column spaces are not the same.

4604
06:31:33,880 --> 06:31:35,480
These matrices are row equivalent,

4605
06:31:35,480 --> 06:31:37,600
but their column spaces are not the same.

4606
06:31:38,600 --> 06:31:44,600
All right, let's look again, same set of matrices.

