06:31:44,600 --> 06:31:47,960
Now, the row spaces are the same because we want a basis

4608
06:31:47,960 --> 06:31:53,200
for the row space of A. Then, right, we look at each row of A.

4609
06:31:53,200 --> 06:31:55,400
Well, they're the same row, right?

