06:40:39,160 --> 06:40:47,760
That means that the columns of A span our end, which again, they can only do that if there's a pivot position in every row,

4753
06:40:47,760 --> 06:40:50,760
meaning there's n pivot positions.

4754
06:40:50,760 --> 06:40:53,960
The dimension of the column space is n.

4755
06:40:53,960 --> 06:40:57,660
That actually falls from number two here.

4756
06:40:57,660 --> 06:41:03,460
If column space of A equals our end, we know that there are n vectors and a basis for our end.

4757
06:41:03,460 --> 06:41:07,060
So therefore, the dimension of the column space is n.

4758
06:41:07,060 --> 06:41:08,460
And the rank of A equals n.

