06:42:52,860 --> 06:42:57,160
Okay, so it's a five by six matrix with four pivot columns.

4775
06:42:57,160 --> 06:43:04,260
Okay, if it has four pivot columns, then that means it has two non-pivot columns.

4776
06:43:04,260 --> 06:43:07,060
So what's the dimension of the null space of A?

4777
06:43:07,060 --> 06:43:08,660
Must be two, right?

4778
06:43:08,660 --> 06:43:11,860
Because you got two non-pivot columns.

4779
06:43:11,860 --> 06:43:14,960
Is the column space of A equal to R4?

