06:51:49,660 --> 06:51:53,460
So it makes sense that the city population is going down.

4858
06:51:53,460 --> 06:51:58,860
We've got more moving to the suburbs than we have coming in.

4859
06:51:59,060 --> 06:52:06,260
To find the suburban population in a year, we could just say, well, since the total is a million,

