06:52:06,260 --> 06:52:12,760
then we can just say a million minus 582,000 and get it that way, which is correct.

4861
06:52:12,760 --> 06:52:16,560
But we could also look at it the way we did with the city and say, well,

4862
06:52:16,560 --> 06:52:26,360
we're getting 5% of the city population moving to the suburbs and 97% of the current suburban population is staying there.

